Columns.Description: Time (UTC) at which this event is generated.
Columns.Name: TimeGenerated

Columns.Description: The correlation ID of the request.
Columns.Name: CorrelationId

Columns.Description: The severity level of the event.
Columns.Name: Level

Columns.Description: Description of the result of the operation, such as 'Received forbidden error'.
Columns.Name: ResultDescription

Columns.Description: The message associated with the error. Includes details on what went wrong and how to mitigate the error.
Columns.Name: Message

Columns.Description: The code associated with the error
Columns.Name: ErrorCode

Columns.Description: The type of event source. It could either be Event hub or IoT hub.

Columns.Description: A unique identifier for the resource that the record is associated with
